# Movie Booking Microservices

Microservice-based Movie Ticket Booking (Spring Boot + Vue.js)

## Tech stack
- Java 21, Spring Boot 3.3, Spring Cloud (Eureka, Gateway, Config)
- MongoDB (Movie), MySQL (Booking/User), Redis (seat hold)
- RabbitMQ (events)
- Docker & Docker Compose, GitHub Actions (CI)

## Project layout


## Quick start (dev)
1. Start databases: `docker-compose up -d mongo mysql rabbitmq`
2. Build & run a service: `mvn -pl movie-service spring-boot:run`
3. Run all with docker-compose later...

